Versatile Makeup Kit: Packed with bold, no-crease shades that glide on your skin like silk, this pen set offers high pigmentation and all-day wear. It doubles up as a contouring and highlighting tool, making it your go-to solution for any makeup scenario.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Experience the vibrancy and versatility of LANGMANNI Eyeshadow Stick! Whether you're getting ready for a day at work or preparing for a night out, our eyeshadow stick provides you with a range of colors to match every mood and occasion. With its buildable and blendable formula, it allows you to create a variety of eye-catching looks. This set is perfect for those who enjoy experimenting with their makeup and strive for a look that's unique and personal. It is crafted to deliver a high color payoff while ensuring the eyeshadow remains crease-proof and lasts all day. Get ready to step up your makeup game with LANGMANNI Eyeshadow Stick!

Eyeshadow Stick Set: This Matte eyeshadow stick set is composed of 8 vibrant colors that highlight your eyes, creating a stunning eye makeup. It not only amplifies the beauty of your eyes,face but also brings an irresistible glow, setting you apart on every occasion. User-Friendly: Designed for a comfortable application without causing any irritation. No need for additional brushes, just swipe it on. It is highly pigmented and retractable, ensuring your eyeshadow stays fresh, dries quickly, and does not fade. The eyeshadow stick is easy to remove and clean. It can also be used as a contouring or highlighting tool, offering a multipurpose solution for all your makeup needs. Sophisticated & Buildable Base Color: Our eyeshadow stick's creamy and soft texture makes blending a breeze, allowing you to create a beautiful finish effortlessly. Even beginners can use this to create a natural look. The eyeshadow stick does not contain overpowering glitter, ensuring a subtle and natural look.

Perfect Gift: Our eyeshadow set, with its 8-color palette, makes for an ideal gift for friends and family on Valentine's Day, birthdays, and other occasions. Perfect for dating, partying, office work, school, or just your everyday makeup needs. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Smooth and subtle colors
reviews.reviewText: Arrived in a nice packing and each stick is induvial wrapped inside the box. Used 3 diff colors so far and I love them, they go on very smooth, stay a good 8hrs .colors are subtle which is what I wanted, the gold is really nice, just enough of a shine but no glare. My eyelids have no itching or other allergic reactions to them, they are great deal for the price. Very nice product

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Colors are much more neutral than the images show.
reviews.reviewText: The product is nice and applies on smoothly but the colors are super muted compared to what the stickers on the bottom show. Mostly all browns with slight tints towards red or gold instead of more vibrantly those colors like the sticker, just heads up when picking the pallet

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this eye shadow!!
reviews.reviewText: Great colors !! So much easier and better than eye shadow in a case !! Easy to bring in your purse!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Colors are not good
reviews.reviewText: I was excited to get these, but I found the colors were strange shades of brown. there is a silver and a couple of light, very shiny but overall I will not use. Not returning, I guess you get what you pay for in this case.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Not as expected
reviews.reviewText: Colors are not as they really appear. The color on the bottom of the tube is not the same color was what shows up on skin. Much much lighter in color.

reviews.reviewText: I like the different colors and the smooth application. What I don't like is that there were more shiny colors than matte. I prefer matte for daytime and shiny for an evening out.
